name: Example House
summary_text: Project Floor Nine, a nine-floor building, features eight rooms arranged into living, sleeping, and utility zones to promote smooth flow between spaces. The living zone centers on a welcoming lounge with TV stand, coffee table, and rug, plus a compact entry space anchored by a wall mirror and lighting. The sleeping zone includes a bed, nightstands, and dresser, while utilities cover a western kitchen and small washroom. A central freestanding cabinet adds storage, yielding a cohesive, neutral, functional layout.
